# LivePlotEngine - Real-Time Data Charting

LivePlotEngine is perfect for building streaming dashboards, sensor data viewers, or performance monitors.

## Features
- Real-time plot updates  
- Line chart with scrollback  
- CLI-based and simple  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_LivePlotEngine.git
cd main_LivePlotEngine
python visualize.py
